a thousand kisses deep is a 2011 film directed by dana lustig and based on a screenplay by alex &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and vadim moldovan . the film , starring dougray scott , jodie whittaker and emilia fox , is a fantastical thriller about a young woman who , via time-travel , pieces together the events that led to her own death . the film premiered at the 2011 raindance film festival in the united kingdom and was released in june 2012 in the united kingdom and ireland . the film was released in the united states on dvd and digital platforms on 6 august 2013 by osiris entertainment .